  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to identify reasons migraine patients stop using triptan
      medications for abortive headache treatment. It is hypothesized that inadequate education of
      the patient at the time of prescribing the triptan is positively associated with triptan
      discontinuation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
